Package: xnviewmp
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         xnviewmp-data (= ${source:Version})
Description: Free software to view, organise, convert graphics
 XnView is a free software to view, organise,
 convert graphics and photos files or
 to create slide show, contact sheet, HTML pages.

